        {
            "date": "2011-06-06 06:42:09", 
            "sentences": [
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "Re: Use check-box instead of Question button", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "It looks like we have fallen into \"technical trap\".", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "Why?", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\"Question button issue\" has multiple problems!", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "It is not just a issue button vs.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "check-box, this is easy part.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "Much bigger problem is: word \"Question\" is confusing and does not tell anything useful to user what is gonna happen.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "That is why there is also a need for \"pop-up info on mouse over\".", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "User could also be confused: What does \"Question\" stands for?", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "If I just want to write my opinion (not asking a question), should I uncheck the question check-box?", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "The \"Question\" text is only technical term (just like 'eth0' for 'Wired network') to tell a program a distinctive conditional to notify lecture about a question asked (message posted) to him/her.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "What we should do is tell user what this option does and this should be done without 'mouser over' text info.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "I see three options (text on check-box instead of 'Question' text):", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "1. Tell what this option does: \"Send question to Classrom.\"", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "2. What is the purpose of this action: \"Notify lecturer about this message.\"", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "3. Both above options together: \"Notify lecturer by sending message to Classrom.\"", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "I have made an attachment.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "Note: I have also added \"Message\" label to describe what input box is all about.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }
            ], 
            "name": "grofaty", 
            "email": "grofaty"
        }, 
        {
            "date": "2011-06-23 14:11:14", 
            "sentences": [
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "Re: Use check-box instead of Question button", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "We may be in a \"technical trap\", but I think it will be OK.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "The issue of what \"Question:\" is for is addressed in the topics set in the classroom and chatroom, so there is context set for it for the user.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "It's also a UI item in itself since some people are using IRC clients.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "There is a space problem--some people will want to reduce the size of the chat area in order to see more of the web and slide windows, and will also reduce the size of the chatroom to get more width for the classroom text.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "For some the chatroom will be the least important of the four widgets and it is therefore important to conserve space there.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "Thanks again, grofaty, for both reporting this and for working on this with us.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "I'm proceeding with it and we can revisit it if it doesn't work out.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }
            ], 
            "name": "jsjgruber", 
            "email": "jsjgruber"
        }, 
        {
            "date": "2011-06-23 14:24:42", 
            "sentences": [
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "Re: Use check-box instead of Question button", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "My thinking is probably too deep into casual end-user GUI thinking and having problems they are facing and I am forgetting that Lernid application is probably not intended for casual users, but for users that know something about computers and can work quite nice if all of the elements of GUI are not extremely simplified.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "This was only an idea, I totally agree you should have a final decision.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }
            ], 
            "name": "grofaty", 
